<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= settings.seoTitle %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="<%= settings.seoDescription %>">
  <meta name="keywords" content="<%= settings.seoTags %>">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com">
  <link rel="preload" href="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com" as="script">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="<%= settings.faviconPath %>" type="image/x-icon">
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.js"></script>
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/aos/2.3.4/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= settings.seoTitle %>" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= settings.baseURL %>" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= settings.logoPath %>" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="<%= settings.seoDescription %>" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="<%= settings.accentColor %>">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="<%= settings.storeName %>" />
  <meta property="og:locale" content="vi_VN" />

  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            'dark': '#0a0a0a',
            'dark-lighter': '#111111',
            'dark-card': '#1a1a1a',
            'dark-border': '#2a2a2a',
            'text-primary': '#ffffff',
            'text-secondary': '#a1a1aa',
            'text-muted': '#71717a'
          },
          animation: {
            'float': 'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
            'pulse-slow': 'pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite',
            'bounce-gentle': 'bounce-gentle 2s ease-in-out infinite',
            'slide-up': 'slide-up 0.8s ease-out forwards',
            'fade-in': 'fade-in 1s ease-out forwards',
            'scale-in': 'scale-in 0.8s ease-out forwards',
            'glow': 'glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate',
          },
          keyframes: {
            float: {
              '0%, 100%': {
                transform: 'translateY(0px)'
              },
              '50%': {
                transform: 'translateY(-10px)'
              }
            },
            'bounce-gentle': {
              '0%, 100%': {
                transform: 'translateY(0)'
              },
              '50%': {
                transform: 'translateY(-8px)'
              }
            },
            'slide-up': {
              '0%': {
                transform: 'translateY(20px)',
                opacity: '0'
              },
              '100%': {
                transform: 'translateY(0)',
                opacity: '1'
              }
            },
            'fade-in': {
              '0%': {
                opacity: '0'
              },
              '100%': {
                opacity: '1'
              }
            },
            'scale-in': {
              '0%': {
                transform: 'scale(0.95)',
                opacity: '0'
              },
              '100%': {
                transform: 'scale(1)',
                opacity: '1'
              }
            },
            'glow': {
              '0%': {
                boxShadow: '0 0 20px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.1)'
              },
              '100%': {
                boxShadow: '0 0 40px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.2)'
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    :root {
      --accent-color: <%=settings.accentColor %>;
      --accent-rgb: <%=accentColorRgb %>;
    }

    body {
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    html, body {
      visibility: visible !important;
      opacity: 1 !important;
    }
    nav {
      min-height: 64px;
    }

    .glass-effect {
      background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.3);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.1);
    }

    .accent-glow {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.15);
    }

    .hover-lift {
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .hover-lift:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 50px 50px;
      animation: float 20s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .gradient-border {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent-color), transparent, var(--accent-color));
      padding: 2px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .gradient-border>div {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .text-accent {
      color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .bg-accent {
      background-color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .border-accent {
      border-color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .particle {
      position: absolute;
      background: var(--accent-color);
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(1) {
      top: 15%;
      left: 10%;
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      animation-delay: 0s;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(2) {
      top: 65%;
      left: 15%;
      width: 2px;
      height: 2px;
      animation-delay: 2s;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(3) {
      top: 35%;
      right: 12%;
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      animation-delay: 4s;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(4) {
      bottom: 25%;
      left: 18%;
      width: 2px;
      height: 2px;
      animation-delay: 1s;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(5) {
      bottom: 55%;
      right: 20%;
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      animation-delay: 3s;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(6) {
      top: 80%;
      left: 80%;
      width: 2px;
      height: 2px;
      animation-delay: 1.5s;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(7) {
      top: 25%;
      left: 75%;
      width: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      animation-delay: 3.5s;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }

    .particle:nth-child(8) {
      bottom: 15%;
      right: 80%;
      width: 2px;
      height: 2px;
      animation-delay: 2.5s;
      opacity: 0.3;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .markdown-body {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .markdown-body h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.3);
    }

    .markdown-body h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .markdown-body h2::before {
      content: '';
      width: 4px;
      height: 1.5rem;
      background: var(--accent-color);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .markdown-body h3 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .markdown-body h4 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .markdown-body p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: #a1a1aa;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .markdown-body a {
      color: var(--accent-color);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .markdown-body a:hover {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
    }

    .markdown-body ul,
    .markdown-body ol {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      list-style-type: disc;
      color: #a1a1aa;
    }

    .markdown-body ul li,
    .markdown-body ol li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .markdown-body ol {
      list-style-type: decimal;
    }

    .markdown-body strong,
    .markdown-body b {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .markdown-body em,
    .markdown-body i {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .markdown-body code {
      background-color: #161b22;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--accent-color);
      border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.2);
    }

    .markdown-body pre {
      background-color: #161b22;
      padding: 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.2);
    }

    .markdown-body pre code {
      background: none;
      padding: 0;
      border: none;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .markdown-body blockquote {
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.25rem 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.1) 0%, transparent 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .markdown-body blockquote p {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .markdown-body hr {
      border: none;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.5), transparent);
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-dark text-white">
  <%- include('partials/navbar', { user, existingUser }) %>

  <%
    let visibleSections = [];
    
    if (settings.displayFeatures && settings.features && settings.features.length > 0) {
        visibleSections.push('features');
    }
    if (settings.displayStats && stats) {
        visibleSections.push('stats');
    }
    if (settings.displayReviews) {
        visibleSections.push('reviews');
    }
    if (settings.aboutUsVisible && settings.aboutUsText && settings.aboutUsText.trim()) {
        visibleSections.push('about');
    }
    if (settings.displayFAQ && settings.faqs && settings.faqs.length > 0) {
        visibleSections.push('faq');
    }
    if (settings.displayCTABanner) {
        visibleSections.push('cta');
    }
    
    // Helper function to get background class
    function getSectionBg(sectionName) {
        const index = visibleSections.indexOf(sectionName);
        return index % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-dark-lighter' : 'bg-dark';
    }
    %>

  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="
    background: linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.25) 0%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85) 30%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.90) 70%,
        rgba(var(--accent-rgb), 0.20) 100%
    );
">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-grid opacity-20"></div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>

      <div class="absolute" style="top: 20%; left: 25%; width: 1.5px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.3; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="top: 45%; right: 30%; width: 1px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.4; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 1.2s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="bottom: 30%; left: 35%; width: 2px; height: 2px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.25; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 7s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 2.3s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="top: 60%; right: 15%; width: 1.5px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.35; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 5.5s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.8s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="bottom: 40%; right: 40%; width: 1px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.3; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 6.5s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 1.8s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="top: 35%; left: 15%; width: 2px; height: 2px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.2; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.3s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="top: 70%; left: 60%; width: 1.5px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.35; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 5.8s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="bottom: 50%; left: 45%; width: 1px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.25; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 6.8s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="top: 50%; right: 55%; width: 2px; height: 2px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.3; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 7.2s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 0.7s;"></div>
      <div class="absolute" style="bottom: 60%; right: 25%; width: 1.5px; height: 1.5px; background: var(--accent-color); opacity: 0.28; border-radius: 50%; animation: float 5.3s ease-in-out infinite; animation-delay: 1.3s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-8" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="800">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/20 rounded-3xl blur-2xl group-hover:blur-3xl transition-all duration-500"></div>
            <img src="<%= settings.logoPath %>" alt="<%= settings.storeName %>" class="relative w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300">
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
          <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight text-white">
            <%= settings.homePageTitle %>
          </h1>

          <div class="flex justify-center my-6">
            <div class="relative w-40 h-1">
              <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, <%= settings.accentColor %>, transparent);"></div>
              <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full blur-md opacity-75" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, <%= settings.accentColor %>, transparent);"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <%= settings.homePageSubtitle %>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1400">
          <a href="/products" class="group relative px-8 py-3.5 bg-accent rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2.5 justify-center overflow-hidden hover-lift">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-white/0 via-white/20 to-white/0 translate-x-[-100%] group-hover:translate-x-[100%] transition-transform duration-700"></div>
            <span class="relative z-10 text-white flex items-center gap-2.5">
              <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag text-sm"></i>
              <span>Xem Sản Phẩm</span>
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right text-sm transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
            </span>
          </a>

          <a href="<%= settings.discordInviteLink %>" class="group glass-effect hover:bg-white/10 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2.5 justify-center hover-lift">
            <i class="fab fa-discord text-[#5865F2]"></i>
            <span class="text-white">Tham Gia Discord</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <% if (reviews && reviews.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="flex justify-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1600">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-2 bg-dark-card/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg border border-white/5">
            <% 
                        const averageRating = reviews.reduce((sum, review) => sum + review.rating, 0) / reviews.length;
                        const fullStars = Math.floor(averageRating);
                        const hasHalfStar = averageRating % 1 >= 0.5;
                        %>
            <div class="flex gap-0.5">
              <% for (let i = 0; i < fullStars; i++) { %>
              <i class="fas fa-star text-yellow-400 text-xs"></i>
              <% } %>
              <% if (hasHalfStar) { %>
              <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt text-yellow-400 text-xs"></i>
              <% } %>
              <% for (let i = fullStars + (hasHalfStar ? 1 : 0); i < 5; i++) { %>
              <i class="far fa-star text-yellow-400/30 text-xs"></i>
              <% } %>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-medium text-sm"><%= averageRating.toFixed(1) %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce-gentle">
      <a href="#features" class="text-text-secondary hover:text-accent transition-colors text-2xl">
        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <% if (settings.displayFeatures && settings.features && settings.features.length > 0) { %>
  <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden <%= getSectionBg('features') %>">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-dark-card px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-medium">Tính Năng</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Tại Sao Chọn <span class="text-accent"><%= settings.storeName %></span>?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Khám phá những gì khiến chúng tôi trở thành lựa chọn đáng tin cậy của hàng nghìn khách hàng
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-<%= Math.min(settings.features.length, 3) %> gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <% settings.features.forEach(function(feature, index) { %>
        <div class="group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="<%= index * 100 %>">
          <div class="relative h-full glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/0 via-accent/0 to-accent/0 group-hover:from-accent/5 group-hover:via-accent/10 group-hover:to-accent/5 transition-all duration-700 rounded-2xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent to-transparent transform scale-x-0 group-hover:scale-x-100 transition-transform duration-500"></div>

            <div class="relative z-10">
              <div class="mb-6 relative w-fit">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/30 to-accent/10 rounded-2xl blur-xl group-hover:blur-2xl transition-all duration-500 scale-110"></div>
                <div class="relative w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/20 via-accent/10 to-transparent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center transform group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 transition-all duration-500 border border-accent/20 group-hover:border-accent/40">
                  <i class="<%= feature.icon %> text-accent text-3xl drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(var(--accent-rgb),0.5)]"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-accent/30 rounded-2xl animate-ping opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-75"></div>
              </div>

              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">
                <%= feature.title %>
              </h3>

              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <%= feature.description %>
              </p>

              <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-transparent rounded-tl-full opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>

      <% if (settings.features.length >= 4) { %>
      <div class="text-center mt-16" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-6">Sẵn sàng trải nghiệm sự khác biệt?</p>
        <a href="/products" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-lift group">
          <span>Xem Tất Cả Sản Phẩm</span>
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-right transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <% if (settings.displayStats && stats) { %>
  <section class="py-20 <%= getSectionBg('stats') %>">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Thành Tựu <span class="text-accent">Của Chúng Tôi</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Những con số thể hiện cam kết của chúng tôi về chất lượng và sự hài lòng của khách hàng.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="glass-effect p-8 rounded-2xl hover-lift group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark-card group-hover:bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 transition-all duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart text-accent text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
              <%= stats.totalPurchases.toLocaleString('en-US') %>+
            </div>
            <div class="text-text-secondary">Tổng Đơn Hàng</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="glass-effect p-8 rounded-2xl hover-lift group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark-card group-hover:bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 transition-all duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-box-open text-accent text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
              <%= totalProducts.toLocaleString('en-US') %>+
            </div>
            <div class="text-text-secondary">Sản Phẩm Có Sẵn</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="glass-effect p-8 rounded-2xl hover-lift group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-dark-card group-hover:bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 transition-all duration-300">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-accent text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
              <%= (thisMonthStats.totalSiteVisits + lastMonthStats.totalSiteVisits).toLocaleString('en-US') %>+
            </div>
            <div class="text-text-secondary">Lượt Truy Cập</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <% if (settings.displayReviews) { %>
  <section class="py-20 <%= getSectionBg('reviews') %> overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-dark-card px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-medium">Đánh Giá Khách Hàng</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Khách Hàng <span class="text-accent">Nói Gì</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Hơn <span class="text-accent font-semibold"><%= totalUsers.toLocaleString('en-US') %>+</span> khách hàng hài lòng tin tưởng chúng tôi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <% if (reviews.length === 0) { %>
      <div class="text-center py-16">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-dark-card rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <i class="fas fa-comments text-accent text-3xl"></i>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">Chưa có đánh giá nào. Hãy là người đầu tiên chia sẻ trải nghiệm của bạn!</p>
      </div>
      <% } else { %>
      <div class="reviews-slider-wrapper relative">
        <div class="reviews-slider flex gap-6">
          <% reviews.concat(reviews).forEach((review, index) => { %>
          <div class="review-card flex-shrink-0 w-[350px]">
            <div class="glass-effect p-6 rounded-2xl h-full flex flex-col">
              <div class="flex text-yellow-400 mb-4 flex-shrink-0">
                <% for (let i = 0; i < review.rating; i++) { %>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <% } %>
                <% for (let i = review.rating; i < 5; i++) { %>
                <i class="far fa-star text-text-muted"></i>
                <% } %>
              </div>

              <div class="flex-grow mb-6">
                <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed break-words overflow-hidden">
                  "<%= review.comment %>"
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="<%= review.discordAvatar %>" alt="<%= review.discordUsername %>'s Avatar" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-dark-border flex-shrink-0 object-cover">
                <div class="min-w-0 flex-grow">
                  <div class="font-medium text-white truncate"><%= review.discordUsername %></div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-text-muted">Khách Hàng Xác Thực</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    @keyframes slide {
      0% {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      100% {
        transform: translateX(calc(-350px * <%=reviews.length %> - <%=reviews.length * 24 %>px));
      }
    }

    .reviews-slider-wrapper {
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .reviews-slider {
      animation: slide <%=reviews.length * 8 %>s linear infinite;
      will-change: transform;
    }

    .reviews-slider:hover {
      animation-play-state: paused;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .review-card {
        width: 300px;
      }

      @keyframes slide {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }

        100% {
          transform: translateX(calc(-300px * <%=reviews.length %> - <%=reviews.length * 24 %>px));
        }
      }
    }
  </style>
  <% } %>

  <% if (settings.aboutUsVisible && settings.aboutUsText && settings.aboutUsText.trim()) { %>
  <section class="py-20 <%= getSectionBg('about') %>">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Về <span class="text-accent">Chúng Tôi</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Tìm hiểu thêm về câu chuyện, sứ mệnh và cam kết của chúng tôi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="glass-effect p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="markdown-body">
            <%- md.render(settings.aboutUsText) %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <% if (settings.displayFAQ && settings.faqs && settings.faqs.length > 0) { %>
  <section class="py-20 <%= getSectionBg('faq') %>">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-dark-card px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-4">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          <span class="text-sm text-text-secondary font-medium">Câu Hỏi Thường Gặp</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Câu Hỏi <span class="text-accent">Thường Gặp</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Tìm câu trả lời cho các câu hỏi phổ biến về sản phẩm và dịch vụ của chúng tôi
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4">
        <% settings.faqs.forEach((faq, index) => { %>
        <div class="glass-effect rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover-lift" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="<%= index * 50 %>">
          <button type="button" class="faq-button w-full text-left p-6 flex items-center justify-between group" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-white pr-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors"><%= faq.question %></span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-accent transition-transform duration-300 flex-shrink-0"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300" style="max-height: 0;">
            <div class="p-6 pt-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed border-t border-white/10 mt-2">
              <%= faq.answer %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    function toggleFAQ(button) {
      const answer = button.nextElementSibling;
      const icon = button.querySelector('i');
      const allFAQs = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-answer');
      const allIcons = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-button i');

      allFAQs.forEach((faq, index) => {
        if (faq !== answer) {
          faq.style.maxHeight = '0';
          allIcons[index].style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
        }
      });

      if (answer.style.maxHeight === '0px' || answer.style.maxHeight === '') {
        answer.style.maxHeight = answer.scrollHeight + 'px';
        icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
      } else {
        answer.style.maxHeight = '0';
        icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
      }
    }
  </script>
  <% } %>

  <% if (settings.displayCTABanner) { %>
  <section class="py-20 <%= getSectionBg('cta') %> relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          Sẵn Sàng <span class="text-accent">Bắt Đầu?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Tham gia cùng hàng nghìn khách hàng hài lòng và khám phá tại sao chúng tôi là lựa chọn đáng tin cậy cho sản phẩm chất lượng.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a href="/products" class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent/90 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-lift flex items-center gap-3 justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i>
            <span>Khám Phá Sản Phẩm</span>
          </a>
          <a href="<%= settings.discordInviteLink %>" class="glass-effect hover:bg-white/10 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover-lift flex items-center gap-3 justify-center">
            <i class="fab fa-discord text-[#5865F2]"></i>
            <span>Tham Gia Discord</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <% } %>

  <script>
    AOS.init({
      duration: 400,
      easing: 'ease-out',
      once: true,
      offset: 100
    });

    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
      anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const target = document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href'));
        if (target) {
          target.scrollIntoView({
            behavior: 'smooth',
            block: 'start'
          });
        }
      });
    });
  </script>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>